Makefile targets:
default: builds the executable, lab4b
dist: builds the tar.gz file
check: runs smoke tests
clean: removes object and text files

Lab4b:
Get a temperature reading every period, with the period being determined by the user. The button stops the program, and other commands can be channeled in such as start, stop, log, scale, and period. Used poll (2) to detect user input. 